universe u

constant obj : Type u

constant Cow : obj
constant Rabbit : obj
constant Squirrel : obj
constant Tiger : obj

constant Big : obj → Prop
constant Red : obj → Prop
constant Young : obj → Prop
constant Sees : obj → obj → Prop
constant Visits : obj → obj → Prop
constant Chases : obj → obj → Prop
constant Kind : obj → Prop
constant Cold : obj → Prop

axiom T1 : Chases Cow Rabbit
axiom T2 : Chases Cow Squirrel
axiom T3 : Big Rabbit
axiom T4 : Red Rabbit
axiom T5 : Young Rabbit
axiom T6 : Sees Rabbit Cow
axiom T7 : Visits Rabbit Squirrel
axiom T8 : Big Squirrel
axiom T9 : Sees Squirrel Rabbit
axiom T10 : Visits Squirrel Rabbit
axiom T11 : Cold Tiger

axiom R1 : Kind Cow ∧ Visits Cow Squirrel → Red Cow
axiom R2 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Rabbit ∧ Visits Rabbit Squirrel → Chases x Rabbit
axiom R3 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Rabbit → Young x
axiom R4 : ∀ x : obj, Kind x ∧ Red x → Visits x Cow
axiom R5 : ∀ x : obj, Visits x Rabbit ∧ Chases x Tiger → Kind x
axiom R6 : ∀ x : obj, Young x → Visits x Rabbit
axiom R7 : ∀ x : obj, Visits x Squirrel → Sees Squirrel Tiger
axiom R8 : ∀ x : obj, Chases x Rabbit ∧ Sees x Tiger → Sees Tiger Rabbit
axiom R9 : ∀ x : obj, Sees x Rabbit ∧ Young Rabbit → Kind Rabbit

theorem tiger_visits_rabbit : Visits Tiger Rabbit :=
begin
  apply R6,
  apply R3,
  apply R2,
  split,
  exact T9,
  exact T7,
end
